channel.title: RuneScape 317 Dumps + 317 Cache
channel.description:
Hello MoparScape,
[b]Note: This is for Emulous.[/b]
Me and my friend Skyru are making an Emulous project. We will be using a Project Insanity client and an Emulous Base (Not PI but the server PI is based from.)
It would be a lot of help if you guys could please post the follows dumps, or links to where people have posted these dumps.
100% RuneScape Shop Dump (317) 100% RuneScape NPC Dump (317) 100% RuneScape Spawn-Config Dump (317) 100% RuneScape Object Dump (317) 100% RuneScape Item Dump (317)
We don't want any items in the server that aren't from the 317 revision.
Also, does anyone have a 100% 317 - 377 Cache? We also want to get a 317 gameframe, so if any of yuo have links to these it would be helpful because I've looked myself and can't seem to find any.
Thanks,
Skyro!
